<div style="color: #65CAFC; font-size: 24px;">How do I add media to Zeega?</div>

You can add images, videos, sounds and more from the web to Zeega with our <a href="#" class="add-media" style="font-size: 12px;">bookmarklet plugin</a>. 
After the bookmarklet is installed, you will see "Add to Zeega" within your bookmarks bar. Once you're on a webpage where you can add media (see next question for details on which sites and types of pages), you click on "Add to Zeega" within the bookmarks bar. You will then see the plugin animate from the right side of the browser with options to add an item.<br><br>
